SIMPLE: emasculation
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: emasculation
<hw>e*mas`cu*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The act of depriving of virility, or the state of being so
deprived; castration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of depriving, or state of being deprived, of
vigor or strength; unmanly weakness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emasculator</ent>⟦br⟧
